String.name: Ultra-Hyper-Fire-Turbo Time
String.tooltip: Feel the fever! Decreases all skill cooldowns by 80%. Greatly increases MP replenishment. Is not active while in dungeons or battlegrounds.

String.name: Blessing of Amarun
String.tooltip: Increases maximum HP for the first venture into the dungeon.

String.name: Baldera's Blessing
String.tooltip: Increases your gathering proficiencies by 30 and shortens your gathering and crafting time.

String.name: Bravery (JPN event buff)
String.tooltip: Increases skill damage by $H_W_GOOD$value2$COLOR_END, and reduces damage taken by $H_W_GOOD$value3$COLOR_END. Additionally increases attack speed by $H_W_GOOD$value$COLOR_END.

String.name: 100% XP Boost (Premium)
String.tooltip: While VIP Pack is in use, increases hunting XP reward by 100%.

String.name: 100% Reputation Boost (Premium)
String.tooltip: While VIP Pack is in use, increases reputation and credits gained by 100%. Does not apply to battleground reputation or credits.
